---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="What We Do" description="Discover bobbin lace making classes with Hedge End Bobbin Lacemakers. Learn from our expert tutor Amanda with beginner-friendly patterns and techniques.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-lace-100 via-cream-100 to-lace-200 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          We Make <span class="text-lace-600">Bobbin Lace</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Get ready to dive into creativity with our amazing Tutor, Amanda! She has crafted 
          an exciting series of patterns specifically for beginners to master essential techniques. 
          The best part? Students can pick and choose their favourite patterns!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Learning Path -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Your Learning Journey</h2>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lace-200 to-lace-400 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-6xl">🐍</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-lace-100 text-lace-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
              <span>Step 1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Basics: Snakes & Bookmarks</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Prepare to immerse yourself in the art of bobbin lace! Your journey begins with 
              engaging patterns designed to introduce you to new stitches. Although some patterns 
              may feature many repetitions, rest assured — this repetition is a method to strengthen 
              your skills and keep your knowledge sharp.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              After you've perfected the snakes, we'll jump into an exciting bookmark that 
              showcases ground stitch and lovely fans! Next, we'll discover the delightful 
              Honeycombe and venture into a whimsical cloth stitch path adorned with playful spiders.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-lace-100 text-lace-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
              <span>Step 2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Navigating Corners</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Prepare to enhance your skills! Building on the techniques you've already mastered, 
              our next exciting project delves into the exhilarating idea of navigating "around a corner."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              You might feel an "uh oh" as you face this challenge, but rest assured — it's simpler 
              than you expect to master that "simple" corner. We'll strengthen this technique with 
              a stunning fan edging, where you'll also discover how to achieve a pretty edge.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lace-300 to-lace-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-6xl">🪭</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Class Schedule -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-cream-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Class Schedule</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold">Tuesday Mornings</h3>
              <p class="text-lace-600">Boorley Green</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Perfect for early birds and retirees</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>All abilities welcome, from complete beginners to advanced</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Equipment available to borrow while learning</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold">Thursday Evenings</h3>
              <p class="text-lace-600">Botley</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Ideal for those with daytime commitments</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>All abilities welcome, from complete beginners to advanced</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Equipment available to borrow while learning</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-lace-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-lace-700 transition-colors">
          Enquire About Classes
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">What to Expect</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lace-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lace-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Learn at Your Pace</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Pick and choose your favourite patterns. There's no pressure — everyone progresses differently!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lace-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lace-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Friendly Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Join a welcoming group of lace enthusiasts. Make new friends while learning a beautiful craft.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lace-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lace-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Expert Guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our tutor Amanda brings years of experience and patience to help you master every technique.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>